              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "4PI1A"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The measured values were normalized to the",
                "known differential scattering cross sections of",
                "carbon, corrected for multiple scattering, and",
                "expressed as a Legendre expansion."
